
function encrypted_hdl_import_wrapper_config(this_block)

  % Revision History:
  %
  %   16-Jul-2009  (16:43 hours):
  %     Original code was machine generated by Xilinx's System Generator after parsing
  %     K:\ipexport\mvi\ccm\v_src\encrypted_hdl_import_wrapper.vhd
  %
